e="width:100%"><p>Arccos Air is a compact wearable that clips to your belt or slides in your pocket. Built-in motion sensors and GPS detect every shot automatically, powered by AI trained on 1.5 billion+ real golf shots. No sensors on your clubs. No phone required. Just play your round while Arccos captures everything in the background.</p><p><br></p><p>Your purchase includes the Arccos Air wearable, a charging case, and one year of Arccos Game Tracking Membership with full access to the Arccos app, including Strokes Gained Analytics, Smart Club Distances, AI Strategy, Green Maps, and more.</p><p><br></p><p>Compatible with iOS, Android coming soon. Works with or without Smart Sensors.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="85cb713f-1cd6-49c5-ac2c-d6e6da6029e4" class="r-1h9hq41" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="5afb1473-424f-4ffa-b39b-645ed0e7a019" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Raavb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-12s4vpw"><div data-rid="d31b283f-cead-4b80-a989-25f0529dcf50" class="r-uxmhhw alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Shipping + Return Policy</p></span></div><div data-rid="c8957974-85f1-4aa9-9810-80da0b27f163" class="r-1j9x5nc" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-1hi9g52" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Raavb2:"><div data-rid="d50d3a0b-fe0e-45d0-a59a-3e941b55dbbd" class="r-ij4vio"><div data-rid="2972bacf-81e8-450d-9b96-965851ef8dc5" class="r-1ug3xij alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Orders typically ship within 1-2 business days. Estimated delivery dates are provided at checkout based on your location.</p><br><p>All Arccos products come with a 30-day money-back guarantee. If you're not satisfied, you can return your product within 30 days of delivery. Customer is responsible for return shipping costs.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="fd9452d2-76c6-4932-8469-258c457a70de" class="r-1j0stx2" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="0c993c99-e54b-4c54-aa93-ea2a2e03275c" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Reavb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-ly5g04"><div data-rid="f4b5ceb1-941a-428a-8e2b-3fbfd521ae84" class="r-7vojh4 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Do I need sensors on my clubs?</p></span></div><div data-rid="d7310949-aa08-4e92-b815-7cde8d7ebf6a" class="r-15pg9n2" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-fkv2v6" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Reavb2:"><div data-rid="d6c143d6-8708-4c32-a762-0e81d8d703af" class="r-1px5kwx"><div data-rid="6c00c29f-3821-4eae-804b-b95b2f330a76" class="r-13zrt1u alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>No, that's now optional. Arccos Air tracks your game automatically without any sensors on your clubs. Every shot is detected by the wearable. Just play. You get full access to Strokes Gained, AI Strategy, Green Maps, and scoring insights. For the deepest club-level insights, many members prefer to also use Smart Sensors — but they're completely optional.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="84330419-6187-4d85-a9cd-538b298e0878" class="r-14p3ain" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid=